# Refactor: Firebase-Only KYC + Simulated Wallet Payments

## Summary
Remove all external KYC (Digio) and payment (Razorpay) dependencies. Replace with:
1. **Two-OTP Firebase KYC**: Phone OTP → Aadhaar number → Second OTP (UIDAI-styled SMS) → Verified
2. **Simulated Firestore Wallet**: Users get random balance + auto-generated UPI ID. Payments are atomic Firestore balance transfers with company escrow account.

